## A Simple Full Screen Video. 
## Only Support the operation of play, pause and stop.

No Finish!!

视频几个关键特性：
压缩率
存储格式/封装技术/容器)(ogg、ogv、mp4、avi等)
编码技术 H.264\ MPEG4\VP9


播放前准备
Note: This is a Pro/Advanced feature only. Movie Textures are animated Textures that are created from a video file. By placing a video file in your project’s Assets Folder, you can import the video to be used exactly as you would use a regular Texture.
Video files are imported via Apple QuickTime. Supported file types are what your QuickTime installation can play (usually .mov, .mpg, .mpeg, .mp4, .avi, .asf). On Windows movie importing requires Quicktime to be installed (download here).

